# Per-finding allowlist for gitleaks scans.
#
# Prefer `gitleaks.toml` [allowlist] path/regex rules for class-level
# exemptions (test fixtures, CLI templates, env templates, docs). Those
# rules are durable across line-number drift from refactors.
#
# Only add entries here for a single unique finding that needs to stay
# while it's being resolved. Entry format:
#   <fingerprint>:<file>:<rule-id>:<line>
# See: https://github.com/gitleaks/gitleaks#gitleaksignore
